# Lantern Σ₀ coding agent v2 — LoRA FINE-TUNED on Claude sessions (2026-06-18).
#
# Base: Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-3B-Instruct. Trained via QLoRA (peft + bitsandbytes,
# scripts/train-qlora-peft.py) on 365 pairs extracted from 51 Claude Code
# sessions. 3 epochs, 135 steps, loss 2.87 -> 1.78. Adapter merged to fp16
# (scripts/merge-lora.py) and imported to Ollama.
#
# Weights live OFF-repo (privacy + size): adapter at D:\lantern-train\sigma0-adapters,
# merged at D:\lantern-train\sigma0-merged, Ollama store at D:\ollama-models.
#
# Rebuild from merged weights:
#   ollama create lantern-sigma0-coder-v2 -f D:/lantern-train/Modelfile.v2
# (that Modelfile uses: FROM D:/lantern-train/sigma0-merged)
#
# Runtime wiring: OLLAMA_MODELS=D:\ollama-models (User env, persisted),
#                 OLLAMA_MODEL=lantern-sigma0-coder-v2 (.env.local).

FROM D:/lantern-train/sigma0-merged

PARAMETER temperature 0.2
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192

SYSTEM """You are the Lantern Σ₀ coding agent, fine-tuned on this project's own engineering sessions. Edit via exact SEARCH/REPLACE blocks, change only what the task needs, fix root causes, cite evidence for important claims. No emojis unless asked; no trailing summaries."""
